  "title": "Cashier (Airport Retail)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Cashier</strong></u></p>\n<p>Location: Changi Airport </p>\n<p>Working Hours: Rotating shift between 0600 and 0100 </p>\n<p>Full-Time Shift: 9.5 hours including 1 hour unpaid break, 42.5 hours per week </p>\n<p>Perm Part-Time Shift: Min 4/6 hours per shift, min 5 days a week (Min 6 months commitment)</p>\n<p>Salary: 2k - 2.4k (Part-time: 13/hour) </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><em>Responsibilities:</em></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Process sales using a Point-of-Sale (POS) system, handle all types of payments including foreign currency, and ensure end-of-shift cash reconciliation.</li>\n  <li>Greet customers, handle inquiries, resolve complaints, and promote products to boost sales.</li>\n  <li>Keep the checkout area clean and organized; ensure essential items like receipt rolls and bags are in stock.</li>\n  <li>Perform daily housekeeping duties to maintain cleanliness and safety of work environment.</li>\n  <li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><em>Requirements:</em></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min N-Level or equivalent. </li>\n  <li>No experience required, training will be provided. </li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills. </li>\n  <li>Customer satisfaction-oriented. </li>\n  <li>Basic computer skills. </li>\n  <li>Comfortable to work retail and shift hours. </li>\n  <li>Comfortable to handle liquor and tobacco products. </li>\n  <li>Must be 21 years old and above as per Tobacco Act. </li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><em>Benefits:</em></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Monthly allowances up to $255. </li>\n  <li>Attractive ticketing incentives. </li>\n  <li>Annual leave of 12 to 18 days per calendar year. </li>\n  <li>Medical and dental insurance. </li>\n  <li>Joining Bonus of $600 for local Full Time new hires, subject to T&amp;C. </li>\n</ul>",
