    "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>LOTTE Duty Free was founded in 1980 and it has been ranked number one in the Korean duty-free industry for more than 45 years. LOTTE Duty Free is operating overseas duty free operations in various countries including <strong>Australia, Guam, Japan, South Korea, New Zealand and Vietnam </strong>and we had landed in Singapore in 2020. LOTTE Duty Free is now in Singapore Changi Airport operating 18 stores across 4 terminals.</p><p>Linkedin: https://www.linkedin.com/company/lotte-tr-singapore</p>",
